title: #92Noon Toys for Tots! Boudreau/Florio/Treadwell/Gleeman
description: PA & Nordo are live from the Toys for Tots drive at Fleet Farm in Lakeville!  Bruce Boudreau joins the show to talk about the Wild's upcoming game with the Anaheim Ducks.  Mike Florio calls in to talk everything NFL.  Vikings wide receiver Laquon Treadwell gives some insight into his time with the Vikings past and present.  Not to mention, much much more throughout the show!
